beer.beer_description:
A Sweet Stout recipe was merged with vanilla and
infused with chillies to give a subtle spiciness. The
result is an aroma of Chocolate and Vanilla, with
the warmth of alcohol and a gentle chilli heat that
gradually rises as the glass empties. Brewed for GABS 2016
